504
00:43:13,766 --> 00:43:16,760
Is that the meaning behind your warning?

505
00:43:18,246 --> 00:43:23,824
Both of you, listen carefully.
Don't bring her name up mindlessly.

506
00:43:23,824 --> 00:43:26,369
