514
00:44:00,548 --> 00:44:03,815
Try it and see if it works on me.

515
00:44:03,815 --> 00:44:10,338
How are we so alike from head to toe?

516
00:44:10,338 --> 00:44:14,114
You and I are both unfortunate.

517
00:44:21,623 --> 00:44:24,420
