560
00:46:51,010 --> 00:46:53,606
Run! Run!

561
00:47:01,329 --> 00:47:02,931
You're crazy!

562
00:47:02,931 --> 00:47:04,811
Why would you hit them on the head?

563
00:47:04,811 --> 00:47:07,643
