567
00:47:14,668 --> 00:47:18,246
Hey, I was actually really scared.

568
00:47:18,246 --> 00:47:20,563
What's so funny?

569
00:47:20,563 --> 00:47:22,097
We're back.

570
00:47:22,097 --> 00:47:24,721
I heard you two got into a fight.

571
00:47:24,721 --> 00:47:25,849
