they'll find out about everything.

602
00:48:57,021 --> 00:49:00,922
Your friend might think
you're in trouble.

603
00:49:00,922 --> 00:49:05,327
Please don't wrap those. I'm going
to change out of this too. I'm sorry.

604
00:49:05,327 --> 00:49:07,146
Okay, sir.

605
00:49:13,831 --> 00:49:17,813
I have an event to go to,
so I can't stay long.

606
00:49:19,936 --> 00:49:21,737
Oh yeah...

607
00:49:26,010 --> 00:49:29,094
I haven't been paying you...

608
00:49:29,094 --> 00:49:31,317
as if I was using you.

609
00:49:31,317 --> 00:49:35,409
It's not much, but it should be enough
for you to spend it for some time.

610
00:49:35,409 --> 00:49:37,255
Are you crazy?

611
00:49:37,255 --> 00:49:40,027
I was going to treat you really
well when we got married.

612
00:49:40,027 --> 00:49:42,929
I never even bought you nice clothes.

613
00:49:42,929 --> 00:49:48,693
