I feel bad.

614
00:49:48,693 --> 00:49:50,568
You heard something, didn't you?

615
00:49:52,871 --> 00:49:54,934
Did you see her?

616
00:50:01,623 --> 00:50:04,135
When did you see her?

617
00:50:04,135 --> 00:50:06,617
