620
00:50:16,603 --> 00:50:18,608
When did you find out?

621
00:50:19,983 --> 00:50:22,092
Sweetheart.

622
00:50:22,092 --> 00:50:24,077
Let's talk later.

623
00:50:24,077 --> 00:50:25,797
You know that...

624
00:50:25,797 --> 00:50:28,559
I love you, right?

625
00:50:28,559 --> 00:50:30,360
I said let's talk later.

626
00:50:30,360 --> 00:50:34,856
It's not because I didn't love you
that I was only taking care of my family.

627
00:50:37,393 --> 00:50:41,438
You treated me so well

628
00:50:41,438 --> 00:50:43,853
that I think I was only
thinking about myself.

629
00:50:48,025 --> 00:50:51,072
I didn't introduce you

630
00:50:51,072 --> 00:50:54,043
to my family because I thought

631
00:50:54,123 --> 00:50:56,612
they would feel bad
about not letting me go.

632
00:50:58,795 --> 00:51:02,592
You lived your life around me

633
00:51:02,592 --> 00:51:10,646
and I treated you however I wanted.

634
00:51:12,025 --> 00:51:17,476
You would stay there
if I told you to stay there...

635
00:51:19,503 --> 00:51:23,692
You would wait here
if I told you to wait here.

636
00:51:23,692 --> 00:51:27,393
You did anything I asked
and I did that because

637
00:51:27,393 --> 00:51:32,177
you felt like part of my family...
Actually more than family...

638
00:51:34,860 --> 00:51:37,523
Because it felt like you were me

639
00:51:37,523 --> 00:51:39,922
and I was you.

640
00:51:41,742 --> 00:51:45,333
I thought to myself,
"I'll treat him well later."

641
00:51:45,333 --> 00:51:48,670
"I'll be good to him
when we get married."

642
00:51:52,206 --> 00:51:54,731
But it's all over if
we are breaking up like this...

643
00:51:54,731 --> 00:51:56,333
If we are breaking up like this...

644
00:51:58,074 --> 00:52:00,896
then I won't be able to see you again.

645
00:52:04,148 --> 00:52:06,152
I'm so sorry.

646
00:52:08,659 --> 00:52:11,271
Why are you doing this?

647
00:52:11,271 --> 00:52:13,161
Do you want to see someone go crazy?

648
00:52:13,161 --> 00:52:15,188
Just swear at me!

649
00:52:15,188 --> 00:52:16,771
Sung Taek.

650
00:52:16,771 --> 00:52:19,068
What did you and that person talk about?

651
00:52:21,773 --> 00:52:23,750
Let's talk later.

652
00:52:39,235 --> 00:52:41,405
<i>Everything changed.</i>

653
00:52:41,405 --> 00:52:44,780
<i>You knew there was an end.</i>

654
00:52:44,780 --> 00:52:53,003
<i>It's okay. I'm thankful for the time
when our love was beautiful.</i>

655
00:52:53,003 --> 00:53:01,172
<i>Before you show me your tears,
get far away from me.</i>

656
00:53:01,172 --> 00:53:05,576
<i>I don't know if I'll hold onto you,
or if I will beg.</i>

657
00:53:05,576 --> 00:53:08,965
<i>Honestly, what I'm afraid of most is...</i>

658
00:53:08,965 --> 00:53:13,610
<i>Give me a last kiss.
Hold me.</i>

659
00:53:13,610 --> 00:53:17,030
<i>I'll wait for you forever.</i>

660
00:53:17,030 --> 00:53:21,422
<i>Even if you're far away,
I can still feel your presence.</i>

661
00:53:21,422 --> 00:53:25,742
<i>You are the only one
I will love forever.</i>

662
00:53:35,168 --> 00:53:37,056
How am I supposed to dance wearing these?

663
00:53:37,056 --> 00:53:39,275
Do you want me to twist my ankle?

664
00:53:42,590 --> 00:53:44,338
Why am I so off rhythm today?

665
00:53:44,338 --> 00:53:47,126
Because your mind is
thinking about something else.

666
00:53:48,422 --> 00:53:50,168
Are you serious?

667
00:53:50,168 --> 00:53:52,530
You want to act like a teacher now?

668
00:53:56,755 --> 00:54:00,494
<i>Don't worry. It won't take long.</i>

669
00:54:06,143 --> 00:54:07,750
<i>[Sung Taek]</i>

670
00:54:08,485 --> 00:54:10,427
Hello?

671
00:54:10,427 --> 00:54:13,019
Yeah. I can leave in 10 minutes.

672
00:54:14,503 --> 00:54:16,253
What's wrong with your voice?

673
00:54:17,889 --> 00:54:20,224
Why didn't you tell me?

674
00:54:20,224 --> 00:54:22,887
Because I knew you
would be mad at me.

675
00:54:22,887 --> 00:54:25,945
I told you I was going to tell her.

676
00:54:25,945 --> 00:54:28,081
She found out that day.

677
00:54:28,081 --> 00:54:31,510
She saw you walking into my house.

678
00:54:31,510 --> 00:54:33,849
Then you should've told me!

679
00:54:33,849 --> 00:54:36,501
Are you yelling at me?

680
00:54:36,501 --> 00:54:38,148
What did you say?

681
00:54:38,148 --> 00:54:40,474
I was a little...

682
00:54:40,474 --> 00:54:42,887
- taken back.
- What did you say to her?

683
00:54:42,887 --> 00:54:46,740
