her debt and to step back. Why?

684
00:54:46,740 --> 00:54:48,141
What?

685
00:54:49,650 --> 00:54:51,668
What did she do wrong?

686
00:54:51,668 --> 00:54:53,927
Did she get dumped
because she did something wrong?

687
00:54:53,927 --> 00:54:56,476
Does a woman have to do
something wrong to get dumped?

688
00:54:56,476 --> 00:54:59,280
Do you know what kind
of person she is to me?

689
00:55:01,965 --> 00:55:04,391
I told you I was going to tell her!

690
00:55:05,764 --> 00:55:07,887
How can you break up without
hurting the person?

691
00:55:07,887 --> 00:55:11,927
