so just forget about her!

692
00:55:11,927 --> 00:55:13,771
As soon as you entered my house

693
00:55:13,771 --> 00:55:17,077
it became impossible for you two
to go back to the way it was.

694
00:55:18,085 --> 00:55:20,527
You told her to think
of this as paying her debt...

695
00:55:20,527 --> 00:55:22,461
Hae Dang is a human being too!

696
00:55:22,461 --> 00:55:23,789
Keep your voice down.

697
00:55:23,789 --> 00:55:28,454
She said when she copied
your voice, your looks, your tone...

698
00:55:28,454 --> 00:55:32,134
She felt like her life was fake too!

699
00:55:32,134 --> 00:55:34,644
To someone like that...

700
00:55:34,644 --> 00:55:37,474
You told her to think of it as
paying her debt and to forget me

701
00:55:37,474 --> 00:55:39,992
because she lived a fake life?

702
00:55:39,992 --> 00:55:43,835
Is this who you really are?

703
00:55:43,835 --> 00:55:45,621
I get it, so stop.

704
00:55:47,222 --> 00:55:52,471
My head feels dizzy because
I'm so jealous right now.

705
00:55:52,471 --> 00:55:54,713
So stop it.

706
00:55:56,559 --> 00:55:59,202
I must really like you.

707
00:55:59,202 --> 00:56:03,467
To still want to be with you even
when you're being this way.

708
00:56:22,023 --> 00:56:25,101
This is the last time I'll let you off.

709
00:56:25,101 --> 00:56:29,588
From now on, don't care about
another woman in front of me.

710
00:56:41,947 --> 00:56:44,568
I'll be responsible for Jung Hae Dang!

711
00:56:44,568 --> 00:56:48,431
She'll be impersonating me
all her life at a cheap cabaret.

712
00:56:48,431 --> 00:56:51,621
And what can you do for her?

713
00:56:51,621 --> 00:56:55,876
