save her is not you, but me.

715
00:57:01,396 --> 00:57:04,021
This is enough...

716
00:57:04,021 --> 00:57:05,869
Calm down.

717
00:57:29,282 --> 00:57:31,173
<i>Let's talk later.</i>

718
00:57:31,173 --> 00:57:33,179
<i>I said let's talk later!</i>

719
00:57:36,648 --> 00:57:39,240
