year long, I still have days like today.

725
00:58:09,347 --> 00:58:17,273
I'm sorry. But I'll make sure to show
you a sexier performance next!

726
00:58:19,603 --> 00:58:21,824
And you know I keep my word, right?

727
00:58:21,824 --> 00:58:23,860
Get ready!

728
00:58:28,295 --> 00:58:34,884
<i>In order to best myself,
