729
00:58:36,012 --> 00:58:42,608
<i>Why do I entertain people
and lose a part of myself?</i>

730
00:58:43,804 --> 00:58:47,344
<i>I don't shout.</i>

731
00:58:47,344 --> 00:58:49,507
<i>Out of the darkness...</i>

732
00:58:56,137 --> 00:59:00,289
<i>Like you.</i>

733
00:59:00,289 --> 00:59:08,934
<i>I'll forget it all, the tears,
our love, and our memories.</i>

734
00:59:08,934 --> 00:59:16,213
<i>There was never a single moment
when our relationship brought me joy.</i>

735
00:59:27,248 --> 00:59:30,144
We can walk around comfortably
because nobody will recognize me

736
00:59:30,144 --> 00:59:32,505
once we leave the country.

737
00:59:34,206 --> 00:59:36,650
Why did you schedule
the flight at this hour?

738
00:59:36,650 --> 00:59:40,327
- What time is it right now?
- It's a little after four.

739
00:59:43,072 --> 00:59:45,092
